as always there only you were not able to see it because of the darkness of overcast skies…', 4528, 0), (139519, 'If you dwell on the negatives, any life can be terrible, regardless of its circumstances.', 6215, 0), (139520, 'The moon, right now, is even bigger than my love for it.', 5066, 0), (139521, 'Defy me not for gleam can only shine in my existence" said Darkness.', 26467, 0), (139522, 'No truly happy person feels the need to stand in front of a mirror and recite that she''s happy. She just is.', 11368, 0), (139523, 'When you always stay positive, you least worry yourself over anything at all! You only take lessons from negative moments of life, and people who seek to change your positive nature to negative! Don’t ever allow your life to be negative just because of people, things and negative occurrences in life, not even for a brief moment! You are you! You are a positive person; stay positive and be happy!', 4606, 0), (139524, 'But why always think the worst of people? What would she be doing to herself if she adopted that attitude to life? It was better to think the best and be wrong than to think the worst and be wrong.', 5958, 0), (139525, 'Being optimistic is the view looking for the best, it comes with the “never give up” attitude.', 5181, 0), (139526, 'The definition of a person who practices visualization and positive thinking, without taking action: a broke loser.', 26468, 0), (139527, 'Today focus on the qualities you like about yourself, focus on the good friends and family members you have around you .feed today with gratefulness . what you focus on I believe will remain constant in your life.', 7741, 0), (139528, 'When we try to find the good in ourselves and others, we pull those good traits up out of hiding and keep them alive, verses pulling out our bad qualities.', 15389, 0), (139529, 'The next time you think something''s too good to be true, remember - so''s electricity and sewerage!', 5266, 0), (139530, 'Dreams get shattered, hopes are belied, aspirations delude and opportunities elude us. Clouds have the power to conceal the sunshine and our radiance fails to ignite positive thoughts unless we embellish our thoughts and emotions, which can be trained to veer into a positive direction.', 7502, 0), (139531, 'A positive mental attitude can improve your health, enhance your relationships, increase your chances of success, and add years to your life.', 6413, 0), (139532, 'The good news is that opportunities for love enter our lives unpredictably, whether or not we’ve perfected self-compassion or befriended our inner critic.', 124, 0), (139533, 'Some people are incapable of judging others. Why? Because they are to busy judging their own insecurities', 26469, 0), (139534, 'The mindset of loss of a loved one is to understand that the loss will never be undone. You must live with it, like it or not. But, to live well, you must turn that loss into something positive. That way, you can become the best version of yourself; scarred, flawed and unstoppable', 8514, 0), (139535, 'Trying not to believe things when in your heart you are almost sure they are true, is as bad for the temper as anything I know.', 2193, 0), (139536, 'Mindfulness removes the emotional fogs of negative thoughts with the light of awareness.', 379, 0), (139537, 'Stay beautiful, tay positive, and remember that you remember in this world.', 26470, 0), (139538, 'If you don''t have a smile, I''ll give you one of mine.', 1471, 0), (139539, 'No one goes through this life unscathed. No matter what one sees in other people''s lives that might seem better than one''s own, that''s only on the surface. No one knows what goes on beneath. Envy is an exercise in futility, since not one person gets out of this life alive.', 26471, 0), (139540, 'There is always a way.', 26472, 0), (139541, 'I would say about 80 to 90 percent of people''s thinking is not only repetitive and useless, but because of its dysfunction and often negative nature, much of it is also 