ree from any negative thoughts.', 2878, 0), (139644, 'I have nothing to lose in life.', 2878, 0), (139645, 'You can either wonder or worry', 2878, 0), (139646, 'Man always need discomfort for awaken.', 2878, 0), (139647, 'The power of thoughts is ecstasy', 2878, 0), (139648, 'I write to shed my sacred sorrows.', 2878, 0), (139649, 'The sacred words are sword of life.', 2878, 0), (139650, 'Success means you have succeeded in overcoming the obstacles and finally realizing the goal.', 2878, 0);
